trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> event occurs when a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> is added or removed from a managed collection of such lists.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>händelsen inträffar när en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>läggs till eller tas bort från en hanterad samling av dessa listor.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>

trans-unit.source: This event is not raised when an individual list element changes its value.
trans-unit.target: Denna händelse utlöses inte när ett element i enskilda lista ändras dess värde.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> event is generated by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService> class when its <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Remove%2A>, <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Add%2A>, and <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Clear%2A> methods are executed.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>händelse genereras av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService>klass när dess <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Remove%2A>, <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Add%2A>, och <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Clear%2A>metoder utförs.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Clear%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Add%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Remove%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: For the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> event, the `relatedObject` parameter will always reference the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Component> that the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> is associated with.
trans-unit.target: För den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>händelse, den `relatedObject` parametern ska alltid referera den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Component>som den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>är kopplad till.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Component> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>

trans-unit.source: The object that is associated with the collection.
trans-unit.target: Det objekt som är associerad med samlingen.

trans-unit.source: A value that specifies whether a <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> has been added or removed from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Ett värde som anger om en <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"> </xref> har lagts till eller tagits bort från samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The collection of list elements after the action has been applied.
trans-unit.target: Mängd element när åtgärden har tillämpats.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects associated with this event.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar mängden <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"> </xref> objekt som är associerade med den här händelsen.

trans-unit.source: The retrieved <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> represents the state of the collection after the event, which involved adding or removing an element, has been applied.
trans-unit.target: Det hämtade <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>representerar tillståndet för samlingen efter den händelse som rör sig att lägga till eller ta bort ett element har tillämpats.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"></xref> that represents the current state of the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"> </xref> som representerar det aktuella tillståndet för samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a flag indicating whether an element has been added or removed from the collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en flagga som indikerar om ett element har lagts till eller tas bort från samlingen av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: Altering the contents of an existing <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> in the collection will not raise a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: Ändra innehållet i en befintlig <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>i samlingen kommer inte att aktivera en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>händelse.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedType"></xref> that indicates the type of change.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedType"> </xref> som anger vilken typ av ändring.

trans-unit.source: Gets the object that that is associated with the collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar objektet som är associerad med samlingen av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: The RelatedObject property enables the programmer to associate an object to an instance of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs> class.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen RelatedObject aktiverar programmerare för att koppla ett objekt till en instans av <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs>klassen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: For the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> event, the RelatedObject property should always reference the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Component?displayProperty=fullName> that the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> is associated with.
trans-unit.target: För den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>händelse egenskapen RelatedObject bör alltid refererar till den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Component?displayProperty=fullName>som den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>är kopplad till.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Component?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>
Den <xref:System.Object>som är associerade med den hanterade <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"> </xref>.</xref:System.Object>
